---
description: Require changelog updates when code changes
alwaysApply: true
---

# Changelog Rule

- Any code change must include changelog update.
- Add new entry to project changelog or create one if missing.
- Keep entry short, factual, and tied to user-visible change.
- If no changelog file exists, create `CHANGELOG.md` at repo root.
- Do not skip changelog for small fixes, refactors, or UI updates.
